This repository ecompasses a fully functional ecommerce website, created with React and NodeJS.

The purpose of this project is to demonstrate core competencies for frontend development;

> General Web Design
> React hooks
> Routing
> Cloud-based Data Retrival (MongoDB)

Users are thus able to interact as they would in everyday ecommerce sites (amazon.com, newegg.ca, etc.);

> Navigate List of products
> Add products to a cart
> User profile, order history, and account creation
> Payment & shipping
